Find which device to be used:

cat /proc/bus/input/devices

Find entry with name "Wireless Controller"
Find its "handler" and enter in the entry on line 40.


Button              ev_type         code

Left stick X        3               0           0 Left/127 Middle/255 Right
Left stick Y        3               1           0 Top/127 Middle/255 Bottom
Left stick push     4               317         0 Released/1 Pressed


Right stick X       3               3
Right stick Y       3               4
Right stick push    4               318
